            <h3>Discord integration</h3>
            <p>CSMM connects your server to Discord via a chatbridge and notifies you when certain events occur. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img id='img-feature-dashboard' src="../../images/meta/feature-dashboard-blurred.png" alt="Second slide">
